ranking_anomalies.name: Adolf Hitler
ranking_anomalies.issue: Controversial placement so high on an influential list

assessment.brief_assessment: A sophisticated and generally well-constructed ranking of historical figures with strong representation across philosophy, science, religion, and politics. The top 25 are particularly coherent and defensible.
assessment.subjective_impression: This looks like a serious scholarly attempt to rank historical influence, with nuanced selections that go beyond simplistic Western-centric narratives.
